Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:vi,0,0,0,karaoke,Tan đi và trở lại ngày mai, đầy những điều chưa biết
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:th,0,0,0,karaoke,ละลายแล้ว กลับไปสู่วันพรุ่งนี้ที่เต็มไปด้วยสิ่งที่ไม่รู้จัก
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:ru,0,0,0,karaoke,Когда он растает, снова наступит завтрашний день, полный неизведанного.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:pt,0,0,0,karaoke,Derretido e de volta ao amanhã - tão cheio de desconhecidos
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:ko,0,0,0,karaoke,녹아버리면 다시 알 수 없는 내일이 찾아와
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:ja,0,0,0,karaoke,ほらまた　わからないことだらけの明日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:id,0,0,0,karaoke,Meleleh, dan kembali ke esok hari yang penuh kejutan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:fr,0,0,0,karaoke,Il a fondu, vers un nouveau lendemain, vers l'inconnu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:es,0,0,0,karaoke,Una vez derretido, nuestro futuro será una interrogación
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:en,0,0,0,karaoke,Melted away, and back to tomorrow — so full of unknowns
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:19.47,ts,____ x-lang:de,0,0,0,karaoke,so schnell geschmolzen und zurückgekehrt ins Morgen, so voller Unwissenheit.
